In [57]:
file['20_Day Moving Average'] = file['Close'].rolling(20).mean()
In [58]:
file['Upper Band']= file['20_Day Moving Average']+ file['Close'].rolling(20).std()
In [60]:
file['Lower Band']= file['20_Day Moving Average']- file['Close'].rolling(20).std()
In [65]:
